# 🚀 Saturday — The World's Best Enterprise Coding Model

## Executive Summary

**Saturday** is a next-generation coding AI model designed to surpass Claude Opus 4.6 and GPT Codex by systematically addressing every known weakness, loophole, and failure point of current market leaders. Built specifically for **MNC-oriented enterprise deployment**, Saturday combines breakthrough architecture innovations with enterprise-grade security, compliance, and reliability.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This document is a strategic blueprint — a complete technical and business specification for building Saturday from concept to deployment.

