## 2. Saturday's Core Architecture

### 2.1 Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "Input Layer"
        A[Developer Prompt] --> B[Context Assembler]
        C[Codebase Index] --> B
        D[Project Config & NFRs] --> B
    end
    
    subgraph "Saturday Core Engine"
        B --> E[Hierarchical Code Graph Engine]
        E --> F{Complexity Router}
        F -->|Simple| G[Fast Path — Distilled Model]
        F -->|Medium| H[Standard Path — Base Model]
        F -->|Complex| I[Deep Path — Full Reasoning Chain]
        G --> J[Security Validation Gate]
        H --> J
        I --> J
    end
    
    subgraph "Validation Layer"
        J --> K[SAST/DAST Scanner]
        J --> L[Compliance Checker]
